p.k: Hawkodile's caught by the Action Police for bodyguarding without an Action License. / Unikitty comes to the conclusion that everyone would be a lot happier if they would just think the way she does, and with Dr. Fox's help, maybe they can! / It's opening night at the Unikingdom Film Festival! / It's Lazy Sunday, and Unikitty and Puppycorn are having such an amazing time hanging out on the couch, they never want to move!
